data.title: Michael Wenczel
data.meta_description: Michael Wenczel is a German former professional footballer who played as a defender. He also holds Hungarian citizenship.
data.text:
Michael Wenczel (born 23 November 1977 in Heilbronn) is a German former professional footballer who played as a defender.[1] He also holds Hungarian citizenship.
